{"type":"answer","id":95309,"parentType":"question","parentId":7247,"uid":22309,"contents":"<b>中国古语云：</b><br>\n<b>吃得苦中苦，方为人上人</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>人上人这个词色彩太强了。</b><br>\n<u>吃得苦中苦</u>（做别人奴隶）<br>\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;之后<br>\n<u>方为人上人</u>（可奴役别人）<br>\n<br>\n把原来的地主打倒，让自己成为新地主。","date":"2019-12-05","agreeCount":47,"discussionCount":0}